metadata.name: Leech Killers #01
metadata.description:
- MISSION:

Kill the unnamed the low life those who have no personality, their origin is not known but at the same time they are native.
They know you just by looking at you but you can't know them because there is absolutely nothing about them worth knowing except the feeling that you have while confronting one; a strong sense of threat, indifference and most of the time silence.

Be careful to really kill these type (the leech) the first chance that you get otherwise the poisonous confrontation will destroy your unconscious which can lead to physical death in most cases.

-----------------------------
Camera: Xiaomi note 8 pro
